**RestTemplate вҖ” calling another service:**

```java
// In order-service, calling inventory-service:

@Service
public class OrderService {
    private final RestTemplate restTemplate;

    OrderService(RestTemplate restTemplate) {
        this.restTemplate = restTemplate;
    }

    public Order placeOrder(OrderRequest req) {
        // 1. Check inventory in inventory-service:
        String inventoryUrl = "http://inventory-service/api/inventory/" + req.productId();
        InventoryResponse inventory = restTemplate.getForObject(
            inventoryUrl, InventoryResponse.class);

        if (inventory == null || inventory.stock() < req.quantity()) {
            throw new InsufficientStockException("Not enough stock");
        }

        // 2. Reserve stock:
        restTemplate.postForObject(
            "http://inventory-service/api/inventory/reserve",
            new ReserveRequest(req.productId(), req.quantity()),
            ReserveResponse.class);

        // 3. Create order:
        return orderRepository.save(new Order(req));
    }
}

// Configuration:
@Configuration
class AppConfig {
    @Bean
    RestTemplate restTemplate() {
        return new RestTemplate();
    }
}
```

